          "Khaldoun  Khelil"
        ],
        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "To dance was your life and after you met Lucrettia it became your unlife as well. Together you travelled acroos Europe and Asia and perfected your art and honed your bodies into perfect instruments.  In India you became obssessed with the mystic Kali Tandava and Yoga.  When Lucrettia left you to your \"pagan\" practices you barely felt her absence.  When you returned to London after almost a century abroad, it was a city transformed and you knew you had to find a more suitable place for your worshipful dance, a place you could build a temple worthy of Kali.  With the help of your mortal allies you made your way to America and travelled as far West as civilization allowed.  In Phoenix Arizona you built your temple and taught your Progeny. You rose to the rank of Harpy and none dared challenge you.  All of that unravelled over the course of a short year in 1994.  One by one your progeny began to die and none of your rivals seemed capabale of the brutallity visited upon their mangled corpses... It was only after your last progeny was found torn to shred that she revealed herself.  You knew it was her all along and she came to your Elysium to sneer and preen.  When you ripped out Lucrettia's throat before the assembled court no one dared to stop you.  When you drank her heart's blood, the other Toreador gathered close and stared in silent but excited horror. When it was all over you had no choice but to relinquish your title as Harpy and call in every boon you'd acquired to save your unlife.  The Prince declared your sire a member of the Sabbat after the fact and forgave your Diablerie.   You moved to LA with your mortal allies and hid among the Anarchs, never embracing again but seeking out those with the gift of movement.  Now that the Anarchs have fallen under Cathayan control, you've become impressed with the New Promise Mandarianite and found more than one Catahyan receptive to your view of the Tandava and have started to study The Howl of the Devil Tiger Charma. Now you look to the resurgent Camarilla of LA for new students and to help your secret allies in the NPM learn more about their plans."
        ],
